text: The best sugar cane drink in this hawker centre. Coffee by the lady boss is superb. Service is great. They offer wide range of beer choices. My must come to drink stall when I’m in 85 hawker centre. Highly recommended..!
Pleasantly surprised by the large ($4) sugarcane available here.
Oh my god one of the worst honey lemon I’ve had in my life it’s just sugar nothing else

Repeat or Not…Repeat. Only rating them for service as how can you get bottled beer wrong. Actually, you can. However, this place is fine. Service was excellent and the beer was cold. $6.5 for a Tiger…not bad
